These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: traveling, reading
Job: photographer, engineer
1. Job:photographer is in an even position##4
2. Job:engineer == Hobby:reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | reading | traveling |
| Job     | engineer    | photographer   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: sprite, lemonade
Sport: rowing, tennis
1. Sport:rowing is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:lemonade is on the left of Beverage:sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | lemonade | sprite        |
| Sport      | rowing  | tennis |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: folk, rock
Nationality: french, thai
1. Nationality:french is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:rock is on the left of Music-Genre:folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | folk |
| Nationality   | french | thai |

